dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's race\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 189}, {\"ngram\": \"the 24-year-old made headlines\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"a photograph\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"Shriever\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"his arms\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"her body\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"the finishing line\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South-East Londoner has since gone on to win numerous other medals, including taking silver in the 2022 UCI BMX Racing World Championships in Nantes.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.99975055437036, \"rank\": 0.0002495078678322263, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"score\": 0.9999615713071586, \"rank\": 3.843016969882067e-05, \"text\": \"Nantes\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The South-East Londoner\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous other medals\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then in February of this year, Whyte won gold at the BMX Racing World Cup in Brisbane, beating Switzerland's Cedric Butti by less than two hundredths of a second.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"score\": 0.9928315591282795, \"rank\": 0.005498254385121284, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7804767730450767, \"rank\": 0.280464892137302, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"Whyte\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the BMX Racing World Cup\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"less than two hundredths\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He now has his sights set on continuing his winning streak at theParisgames.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"his winning streak\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisgames\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Below, we chatted to Whyte about what makes BMX such a stand-out sport and why, despite numerous injuries and setbacks, he always returns to it.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whyte\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous injuries\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"setbacks\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was watching on the television the 2008summerOlympics inChina.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the television\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2008summerOlympics inChina\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was when BMX made its Olympic debut and I remember being so excited to watch it.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was sat watching Liam Phillips compete as part of Team GB and thinking that is exactly what I want to do.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liam Phillips\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\"}, {\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999992422461361, \"rank\": 6.243059936920003e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was around eight years old at the time and that was my goal, to get to the Olympics no matter what.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"my goal\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BMX racing is such a unique sport.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.217683593656669e-13, \"text\": \"BMX racing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a unique sport\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I absolutely love the speeds we can go up too and the fact it is super-fast which is really exhilarating.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the speeds\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is one of the most dangerous sports and that's what I love; the danger element pushes me on to go further.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most dangerous sports\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1432}, {\"ngram\": \"the danger element\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when I win a race it is all worth it.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not really find anything hard about it but you have to have the right mind set and concentration.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"the right mind\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your goal is to race fast and always think about not falling off your bike at the same time.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your goal\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"your bike\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always have to be focussed.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is good to start at a young age if you like BMX riding, but there are people who develop a passion for it later in life.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"a passion\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd really recommend getting involved in your local BMX club and there you can take part in training sessions and learn the basic skills.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"training sessions\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the basic skills\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, if you are good enough, you can start competing in club races locally, then regional ones.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"club races\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"regional ones\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are local clubs all around the country who can teach you everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local clubs\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got my first taste of racing at the Peckham BMX Club, where my dad was a coach.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7282900883381945e-24, \"text\": \"Peckham\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first taste\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a local club, it is excellent and helped teach me so much.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a local club\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know my victory at the Olympics has inspired the next generation of BMX riders at the club too.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my victory\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew from a very early age I was going to make it as I felt so confident on the bike.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very early age\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was around ten year's old and was winning races against boys who were four years older than me.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I won lots of British junior titles and so I knew I was good at what I did.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9986459663736788, \"rank\": 0.0012604435892965248, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing you are good at what you do powers you on to success.\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely has to be the numerous Injuries I have sustained from falling off the bike.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the numerous Injuries\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had so many accidents and setbacks during my recovery.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many accidents\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"setbacks\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"my recovery\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have broken both my collarbones, shoulders, my wrist, fingers and the worst accident happened when I was 13 years old.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both my collarbones\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulders\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"my wrist\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"fingers\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3009}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst accident\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I fell off the bike badly, broke my jaw and had a bleed on my brain.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"my jaw\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"a bleed\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"my brain\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in an induced-coma for days and it was a very worrying time as I could have died.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an induced-coma\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"a very worrying time\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not compete for a year after that accident.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\":